{"tid":1128271,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一計救杜汶澤","createTime":"2019-04-27T17:03:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T14:20:53.000Z","uid":36708,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6f3018193cc801a1a11e1683a27bf824cc06d8f7","tid":1128271,"uid":36708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T17:03:45.000Z","msg":"呢件事就擺明杜汶澤又柒又小氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條女應得嘅人工俾人拖左幾個月<br />\n已經好聲好氣問個豪仔，條友做嘢又冇交帶<br />\n又俾杜生不明不白咁開全名黎屌，真係好撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都幾慶幸兒登仔係大是大非面前唔會盲目反雞撐杜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一人一計幫兒登契爺杜汶澤走出困局<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n拋磚引玉：<br />\n炒撚左豪仔，請條女頂豪仔個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條女反擊列點point point 有力，態度不亢不卑，做野幾有交帶，反擊前仲會通知聲豪仔，做幕後好過賣肉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b147c75ab5f1af84391bd7490074bc0a86299e1","tid":1128271,"uid":50779,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T17:05:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ea8cf8f73cb8aa39a1648f8f065e6c9da599be6e","tid":1128271,"uid":126133,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T17:07:06.000Z","msg":"唔理佢就得，過幾日邊個理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f0e9f6df237f4b1b65d0be66a8f14d1e7d0b3fb","tid":1128271,"uid":45774,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T17:16:34.000Z","msg":"佢最叻柒咗就玩失蹤<br />\n到件事淡咗又出返黎講幾句粗口扮型"},{"pid":"48d35ef40e918ed32044a24d3933ee2afd87dc7f","tid":1128271,"uid":22694,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"0f0e9f6df237f4b1b65d0be66a8f14d1e7d0b3fb","tid":1128271,"uid":45774,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T17:16:34.000Z","msg":"佢最叻柒咗就玩失蹤<br />\n到件事淡咗又出返黎講幾句粗口扮型"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T17:18:06.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n次次都一樣嘻嘻哈哈扮冇事"},{"pid":"69f576dbd4852512bb711656bb966b838a75d5f0","tid":1128271,"uid":220701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T17:19:48.000Z","msg":"唔緊要啦 反正臉皮厚就可以當冇事發生"},{"pid":"cff032c37a957935daa8b44624aac50de81890fb","tid":1128271,"uid":11880,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T17:21:30.000Z","msg":"賴撚哂落豪仔度咪得囉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過學番你自己話齋<br />\n邊個仲敢打你工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b18d31491599aebbaf25ebec1c1771cdbfdbfecb","tid":1128271,"uid":36708,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"0f0e9f6df237f4b1b65d0be66a8f14d1e7d0b3fb","tid":1128271,"uid":45774,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T17:16:34.000Z","msg":"佢最叻柒咗就玩失蹤<br />\n到件事淡咗又出返黎講幾句粗口扮型"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T17:23:49.000Z","msg":"如果真係咁，咁呢件事真係完美演繹左誰大誰惡誰正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對杜汶澤好失望，一個大男人未搞清楚件事去開晒名咁鬧一個賣肉嘅暗星，食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ae8484cd041152f6b87175dd9f3b033b0678dba","tid":1128271,"uid":199505,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T17:25:25.000Z","msg":"賴落田蕊妮度，老婆見個整容雞姣鳩杜生因愛成恨，然後慫恿豪仔米撚出糧比佢，搞場大龍鳳出黎，臭雞收皮，杜生收山靠佢養唔會搞搞震，一本萬利"},{"pid":"a93e9c99dece6085a5d1ca41f8b17620ee5bc9f9","tid":1128271,"uid":133525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T17:26:32.000Z","msg":"個2字好心佢整得好啲啦，呃人都用下個死人腦啦"},{"pid":"93b262573f6a7d6ec3c7475e455b48453282da6b","tid":1128271,"uid":137217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T17:36:55.000Z","msg":"佢block q咗comment啦<br />\n入面無剷果幾個留言都整到件事好似唔關佢事咁"},{"pid":"1f1be8ad3d65a163e55df170b061e68bf5650c29","tid":1128271,"uid":199957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T17:41:18.000Z","msg":"杜生出黎開記招 流下眼淚鼻涕<br />\n話自己壞左 對唔住大家<br />\n之後當冇事"},{"pid":"011ffecc8c80db4ee6cf1a01ae46379d11d1da72","tid":1128271,"uid":36708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"93b262573f6a7d6ec3c7475e455b48453282da6b","tid":1128271,"uid":137217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T17:36:55.000Z","msg":"佢block q咗comment啦<br />\n入面無剷果幾個留言都整到件事好似唔關佢事咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T18:04:35.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時聲大夾惡<br />\n自己柒冤枉咗一個暗星<br />\n間接謀殺左佢嘅事業<br />\nSo99y都唔講一句<br />\n正垃圾"},{"pid":"278d6d3ed8645f20fec92fc86ee8ec77203b1a23","tid":1128271,"uid":202698,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T18:16:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190427/large/1556374550_854c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190427%2Flarge%2F1556374550_854c.jpg&h=5c2f9f4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n經撚典，自己用PS都唔用好D，粒格仔咁明顯<br />\n而且邏輯都唔撚通，有10/4問拎銀行資料，但可以4號就入左數<br />\n<br />\n如果當時入左數，咁問洗托柒？？<br />\n10/4先俾銀行資料佢，但4/4就入左數，即係一拎完資料，就坐時光機返去入數？"},{"pid":"752be17b35baee1dc80754f195b796c1336bf2f2","tid":1128271,"uid":50882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T19:39:12.000Z","msg":"一齊拍個轉數快廣告 嘻嘻哈哈咪冇事囉"},{"pid":"d29898c54474b268bc95509f67dd2875bedd52e5","tid":1128271,"uid":36708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T14:17:42.000Z","msg":"杜生止蝕喇，今鋪你柒出宇宙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbd3095c5f2d0af0ea98edd9f5581283665b474a","tid":1128271,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T14:19:27.000Z","msg":"阿澤：我係娛樂圈二十年 我會輸比條靚妹？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33f1a8ef41ccc3aa0c95b080e48ccef2e31d621f","tid":1128271,"uid":8636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T14:20:53.000Z","msg":"Fb block 撚左留言咪得囉<br />\n都踩唔到上去架啦"}]}